# Test API Endpoints
# Use REST Client extension in VS Code or Postman

### Register User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "employee",
  "department": "IT"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Create Leave Request (Replace YOUR_TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/leaves
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

{
  "leaveType": "paidLeave",
  "startDate": "2026-03-01",
  "endDate": "2026-03-05",
  "reason": "Family vacation"
}

### Get My Leaves
GET http://localhost:5000/api/leaves/my-leaves
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Get Pending Leaves (Manager/Admin only)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/leaves/pending
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

### Approve/Reject Leave (Manager/Admin only)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/leaves/LEAVE_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

{
  "status": "approved",
  "comments": "Approved for vacation"
}
